    "intro": {
      "whatIs": "What is Nexora Desktop?",
      "description": "Nexora Desktop is a native multiplatform application for professional video processing. It provides GPU-accelerated transcoding, broadcast-standard audio normalization (EBU R128), perceptual quality scoring (VMAF), and a complete 8-stage quality control pipeline.",
