        "vmafDesc": "Perceptual quality measurement comparing source vs. output. Scores above 90 are broadcast-grade.",
        "profiles": "Profiles",
        "profilesDesc": "6 built-in presets (Broadcast HD/SD, Web 4K/HD, Proxy, Social) plus a full custom profile editor.",
